Blocks.Text: CORPORATE ASSIGNMENT OF DEED OF TRUST
Assignor: SRP 2013-2, LLC, at 601 BRICKELL KEY DR., STE 700, MIAMI, FL, 33131
Assignee: WILMINGTON SAVINGS FUND SOCIETY, FSB, NOT IN ITS INDIVIDUAL CAPACITY BUT
SOLELY AS TRUSTEE FOR ATC2021 TRUST, at C/O RICHLAND & FALKOWSKI PLLC, 5 FAIRLAWN DRIVE,
For value received, the Assignor does hereby grant, sell, assign, transfer and convey, unto the above-named
Assignee all interest under that certain Deed of Trust Dated: 7/6/2005, in the amount of $20,250.00, executed by
LISA ROBINSON, A SINGLE PERSON to SWARTZ & BROUGH, INC. and Recorded: 8/19/2005, Instrument #:
123739, Book: 752, Page: 125 in TRINITY County, State of Texas.
TO HAVE AND TO HOLD, the same unto Assignee, its successors and assigns, forever, subject only to the terms
and conditions of the above-described Deed of Trust.
On February 09, 2022, before me, Jessica Brown, a Notary Public in and for STONE in the State of MISSOURI,
personally appeared KALEENA OGO, ASSISTANT VICE PRESIDENT, SRP 2013-2, LLC, personally known to me
(or proved to me on the basis of satisfactory evidence) to be the person(s) whose name(s) is/are subscribed to the
within instrument and acknowledged to me by means of X physical presence or online notarization, that
he/she/they executed the same in his/her/their authorized capacity, and that by his/her/their signature on the
instrument the person, or the entity upon behalf of which the person acted, executed the instrument.
WITNESS Jessica my hand and official seal,
- wer dify RECORDED the Official Resords
